OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright
OL,6,Fspells and the odd shower during this
OL,7,Fevening. Showers will continue across
OL,8,Fthe northwest overnight but becoming
OL,9,Fdry with variable amounts of cloud
OL,10,Felsewhere.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FDry and bright in the
OL,13,Fnortheast at first. Cloud and rain,
OL,14,Fsome heavy, soon spread northeast in
OL,15,Fthe morning. Turning drier in the
OL,16,Fafternoon but showers developing in
OL,17,Fthe northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
